snippet: A court case filed by Precision Cars India, an auto importer, has led to warrants for nine Porsche executives and calls by the Indian government for help from Interpol.
abstract: A court case filed by Precision Cars India, an auto importer, has led to warrants for nine Porsche executives and calls by the Indian government for help from Interpol.

headline.main: Indian Court Issues Warrant for Porsche C.E.O.'s Arrest
headline.print_headline: India Seeks To Arrest Chief Of Porsche
